<L>__{exterior snowplow roadside night}
<A>__{the instant she sets foot outside she stops dead, the blood rushing from her face and her eyes going wide in disbelief. pan 360 degrees to reveal a landscape she knows all too well: the stranded `88 oldsmobile. the telephone pole she climbed. they haven't gone anywhere. no time to puzzle it out. the sound of the snowplow driver making his way down the embankment o.s. stirs her to action.}
